{"tid":1862232,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[全民三罷] 醫護工會並不代表所有 醫護，以及 香港人","createTime":"2020-02-04T13:46:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T00:40:37.000Z","uid":73143,"like":126,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"e609208b7bcfac328da4dcef548d81b7673e8a2e","tid":1862232,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:46:12.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>上醫醫國，中醫醫人，下醫醫病</strong></span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">鑑於太多吹風唔罷<br />\n我想講既係醫護罷工起左個頭後，好多工會都準備緊<br />\n香港人要做既係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全港大三罷</span></span></strong><br />\n直至政府做返本身佢應該要做既事，甚至係五大訴求<br />\n成個制度已經由內至外腐爛，一日唔改變都只會有同樣既事情發生<br />\n而唔係咩社區大爆發之後成班返去醫院醫病</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">醫護工會並不代表所有醫護，以及 香港人<br />\n<br />\n妥協只會失敗</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mvysk2D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmvysk2D.jpg&h=2ebcbca0&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"6dd12a48993c1cccfc1a9a3926cf1acc457278a8","tid":1862232,"uid":73143,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:51:09.000Z","msg":"全民三罷 刻不容緩"},{"pid":"2b7ee4c72c2055ab7532c60c33c35c1862801a8f","tid":1862232,"uid":51411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:52:13.000Z","msg":"大三罷要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"609b90f3229655eb4e5cfb31017720f2f529833e","tid":1862232,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:52:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"564987ec88adec100fa204c89971696143ac3a73","tid":1862232,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":