me":"2020-02-04T14:57:58.000Z","msg":"假cert黎嫁？ <br />\n黑白？"},{"pid":"bf740b10d0033fe7cc5d437aff089956159a0f96","tid":1862232,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:59:36.000Z","msg":"全民三罷 刻不容緩"},{"pid":"c1b945a74164e4f3de4cc3352af14ad7881ebbcb","tid":1862232,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:11:09.000Z","msg":"全民三罷 刻不容緩"},{"pid":"783dbde6bf2c755823ceb155bdae3d5a15c4a29c","tid":1862232,"uid":73143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"55340eed8ec0f4fba008d93bbbe10c0f109e274c","tid":1862232,"uid":60000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e609208b7bcfac328da4dcef548d81b7673e8a2e","tid":1862232,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:46:12.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>上醫醫國，中醫醫人，下醫醫病</strong></span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">鑑於太多吹風唔罷<br />\n我想講既係醫護罷工起左個頭後，好多工會都準備緊<br />\n香港人要做既係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全港大三罷</span></span></strong><br />\n直至政府做返本身佢應該要做既事，甚至係五大訴求<br />\n成個制度已經由內至外腐爛，一日唔改變都只會有同樣既事情發生<br />\n而唔係咩社區大爆發之後成班返去醫院醫病</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">醫護工會並不代表所有醫護，以及 香港人<br />\n<br />\n妥協只會失敗</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mvysk2D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmvysk2D.jpg&h=2ebcbca0&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:57:58.000Z","msg":"假cert黎嫁？ <br />\n黑白？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tzWp8d0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtzWp8d0.png&h=12ec3a53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8edf2ac3a3449f28faa6272d691fa43a48453a2","tid":1862232,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:16:12.000Z","msg":"全民三罷 刻不容緩"},{"pid":"710afbcff4223ceb5fc72f9238c705b61cea941a","tid":1862232,"uid":60000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"989adfd7525026e17713f6d7f8d13a4b88c01a20","tid":1862232,"uid":217430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:02:07.000Z","msg":"各行業請緊隨醫護手足的步伐。複製醫護罷工的成功方程式。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">一.成立公會</span><br />\n並高調召開會員大會表決罷工，一定要有直播影著過程。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">二.開口牌</span><br />\n簽署罷工宣言承諾罷工。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">三.全民醒覺</span><br />\n大家放心。已經有八成香港市民支持全面封關。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">罷工救港<br />\n全面封關</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:16:27.000Z","msg":"市民支持有鬼用阿"},{"pid":"ff0804f4d5c5ee8fb87588579fb95f32323ad7c0","tid":1862232,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:18:46.000Z","msg":"全民三罷 刻不容緩"},{"pid":"7cf88e47ecdb16d99fa54cb3d72dfa3313dc4c68","tid":1862232,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:19:53.000Z","msg":"突然間大量p牌同五毛狗+真心膠係度帶風嘅<br />\n表示而家爆發左就封關都無用<br />\n叫醫護復工<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n實情係同機場果招一樣<br />\n佢地無法破<br />\n就等大家自己放棄<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家一定唔可以再中港共依招<br />\n<br />\n罷到底<br />\n<br />\n唔從源頭開始減少<br />\n<br />\n做死都幾多醫護都無用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我希望大家可以明白依個道理<br />\n同埋堅定醫護個心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">希望各行各業而家開始配合埋港鐵工會同巴士公會<br />\n發展成全港大罷工<br />\n情願日日都係年初一<br />\n都好過武漢咁日日死城</span></span>"},{"pid":"7030b168f1e3c5620571a0ad0c7a8b61fe2f2425","tid":1862232,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:24:01.000Z","msg":"全民三罷 刻不容緩"},{"pid":"d1cfdee11b896204c30bc8003b19e62b497b57b1","tid":1862232,"uid":47710,"like